---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Terms of Service | Tropic Wings Transfers"
  description="Terms of Service for Tropic Wings Transfers — Cairns Airport to Port Douglas transfer service operated by Tropic Wings Cairns Tours & Charters."
  canonical="/terms"
>
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-8 py-16">
    <nav class="text-on-surface-variant text-xs font-label mb-8 flex items-center gap-2">
      <a href="/" class="hover:text-primary transition-colors">Tropic Wings Transfers</a>
      <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">chevron_right</span>
      <span>Terms of Service</span>
    </nav>

    <h1 class="text-4xl font-headline font-black tracking-tighter text-on-surface mb-4">Terms of Service</h1>
    <p class="text-on-surface-variant font-body text-sm mb-12">Last updated: April 2026</p>

    <div class="space-y-8 font-body text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-headline font-bold text-on-surface mb-3">1. Operator</h2>
        <p>These terms govern the use of transfer services provided by Tropic Wings Cairns Tours &amp; Charters Pty Ltd ("Tropic Wings", "we", "us") via transfers.tropicwings.com.au.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-headline font-bold text-on-surface mb-3">2. Bookings</h2>
        <p>Bookings are confirmed upon receipt of full payment. You will receive a booking confirmation by email. Please check all details and contact us immediately if anything is incorrect.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-headline font-bold text-on-surface mb-3">3. Cancellation and refunds</h2>
        <p>Cancellations made more than 24 hours before departure are eligible for a full refund. Cancellations within 24 hours of departure are non-refundable. No-shows are non-refundable. To cancel, email <a href="mailto:info@tropicwings.com.au" class="text-primary hover:underline">info@tropicwings.com.au</a> or call +61 7 4041 9400.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-headline font-bold text-on-surface mb-3">4. Flight delays</h2>
        <p>We monitor Cairns Airport (CNS) arrivals. If your flight is delayed, contact us as soon as possible and we will transfer you to the next available departure at no additional charge, subject to availability.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-headline font-bold text-on-surface mb-3">5. Luggage</h2>
        <p>Each passenger may bring one standard suitcase (max 23kg) and one carry-on bag. Oversized or additional items must be declared at booking. We reserve the right to decline carriage of items that cannot be safely carried.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-headline font-bold text-on-surface mb-3">6. Liability</h2>
        <p>Our liability is limited to the cost of the transfer. We are not liable for loss of property left in vehicles, missed flights, or consequential losses. Travel insurance is strongly recommended.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-headline font-bold text-on-surface mb-3">7. Conduct</h2>
        <p>We reserve the right to refuse carriage to any passenger whose conduct is disruptive, offensive, or endangers the safety of other passengers or our driver. No refund will be issued in such cases.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-headline font-bold text-on-surface mb-3">8. Governing law</h2>
        <p>These terms are governed by the laws of Queensland, Australia. Any disputes are subject to the exclusive jurisdiction of the courts of Queensland.</p>
      </section>

    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
